Similar words:

Spa and Massage are similar words because they both refer to places where people go to relax and receive body treatments.
Apple and Computer are similar words because they are both products of the Apple company.
Similar documents:

Doc 1 and Doc 2 are similar documents because they both have high counts for the words Spa and Massage. This suggests that they are both about spas or massage parlors.
